{"tid":1494732,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"821有出現過的入一入來！","createTime":"2019-08-21T18:20:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T06:00:55.000Z","uid":219635,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"60756d2c3e4767aee9eeda4fe2e954c584263c65","tid":1494732,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T18:20:21.000Z","msg":"其實今晚我有好多野想講，首先，7點開始集會去到近10點鐘黑警就玩清場仲有警黑合作又入村保護黑社會絕對係無法無天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，當時仲有好多市民，街坊同手足在場。好多人成日都話呢排和理非主場，勇武手足似乎已經退場/有減退跡象。<br />\n但其實唔係！一切都只係幻象同5毛想帶風向，由170萬人上街示威已經知道，其實和勇係仍然存在。點解咁講？今晚821元朗集會就係一個示範！<br />\n好多勇武手足都肯出現，當好多和理非，市民同區議員仲係到播片同上台演講加靜坐時，<span style=\"color: red;\">你地就係附近做路障做巡邏，呢個行為絕對係和勇合作的最佳演繹，好多謝大家仍然不割蓆，不分化。</span>仲好似互相配合咁，你有你上台播片，我有我做巡邏保衛工作。比起以往一般示威遊行都係完左先由勇武進場的做法更新穎同合作。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但有一樣野想講都係，和理非同食花生市民可唔可以唔好行咁前，因為真係會塞住勇武手足的去路，仲有成日大驚小怪，黑警一有咩風吹草動就大叫：走佬，全世界鬥快跑上地鐵站咁。到有畜龍追上變相令前線落單手足機會增加，因為仲要顧在場和理非及市民街坊先走而有手足落單。</span><br />\n都係果句，前線話走先真係走，唔好亂走叫影響風向，同埋人多的勇武就可以救到落單手足架，個個掛住走佬咁樣冇人理勇武手足就好快比人拉哂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不分化！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ad2da099517db5bc2f66f2ceed0c6b910d07476","tid":1494732,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T18:22:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12cf481b590423289bcf11e379b8e2b50454bfd5","tid":1494732,"uid":228437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T18:37:32.000Z","msg":"真。<br />\n我一直坐在和理非中，有事即跑入廁所上gear，有和理非仲幫我擺好啲野，然後即上前線<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b690ae9ae146d2cdb89e6212eb50db374cd800a","tid":1494732,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12cf481b590423289bcf11e379b8e2b50454bfd5","tid":1494732,"uid":228437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T18:37:32.000Z","msg":"真。<br />\n我一直坐在和理非中，有事即跑入廁所上gear，有和理非仲幫我擺好啲野，然後即上前線<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T18:39:09.000Z","msg":"和理非除左走佬仲有好多可以做，和勇合作仲係萌芽初期中，大把野改善緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f56ff45723937dc8acf38635b49c9cf49a337232","tid":1494732,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T18:40:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44208353f08e1715a3b711df02e550ac6ebe4c73","tid":1494732,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T18:41:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />黑警今晚又保護黑社會"},{"pid":"d71b3af5e851f167fd46fd8085f7935c6524631c","tid":1494732,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44208353f08e1715a3b711df02e550ac6ebe4c73","tid":1494732,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T18:41:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />黑警今晚又保護黑社會"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T18:49:32.000Z","msg":"文宣重點工作：警黑合作入村同趕記者出村<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d9ed6ab6641b8242eb0521471e8cd55a139589a","tid":1494732,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T18:49:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53d5a4e718b0d8b2d865aced9d193bf934b4ec77","tid":1494732,"uid":63311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T18:50:07.000Z